planHighlights:
Highlights
If you live in a long term care facility such as a nursing home, this plan may be a good fit for you. You can receive the extra attention of a nurse practitioner who will help coordinate your care.
• Low premium.

• Covers care you receive through our network of local doctors and hospitals.

• Care can be received out of our network but usually at a higher co-pay or co-insurance.

• No referral required to see specialists.

• Includes prescription drug coverage.
